But in this vast desert,

573
00:26:29,540 --> 00:26:30,700
where can we find such a person?

574
00:26:31,580 --> 00:26:32,500
The arts of war

575
00:26:33,020 --> 00:26:33,860
are exquisite.

576
00:26:35,340 --> 00:26:37,060
It's fair that I need some time

577
00:26:37,620 --> 00:26:38,740
to understand it.

578
00:26:40,220 --> 00:26:41,300
It hasn't been long

579
00:26:41,300 --> 00:26:42,540
since I led my troops westward,

580
00:26:43,140 --> 00:26:44,220
and you have already gathered troops

581
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:45,060
to arrive at this place.

582
00:26:46,260 --> 00:26:47,260
If it weren't for someone

583
00:26:47,260 --> 00:26:48,380
in the Mongol army
to inform you in advance,

584
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:50,660
how could you

585
00:26:50,660 --> 00:26:52,060
hear the news so quickly?

586
00:26:52,980 --> 00:26:53,820
And

587
00:26:54,380 --> 00:26:55,260
who else

588
00:26:55,260 --> 00:26:56,580
can mobilize the Beggars' Gang

589
00:26:56,580 --> 00:26:57,580
and the heroes of Taihu Lake?

590
00:26:58,300 --> 00:26:59,140
Also,

591
00:27:00,660 --> 00:27:02,580
Chief Huang's life is uncertain,

592
00:27:03,660 --> 00:27:04,820
but you're helping me

593
00:27:04,820 --> 00:27:06,100
attack the Jins here calmly.

594
00:27:07,620 --> 00:27:08,460
Therefore,

595
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:09,860
Ouyang Feng

596
00:27:10,100 --> 00:27:11,340
said confidently

597
00:27:12,060 --> 00:27:13,420
that Rong is in the Mongol camp.

598
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:15,700
It's not fully fanciful.

599
00:27:18,820 --> 00:27:19,660
Brother Lu.

600
00:27:21,500 --> 00:27:22,460
You know

601
00:27:22,460 --> 00:27:23,980
I've been looking for Rong
for a long time.

602
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:26,260
Hurry and take me to see her.

603
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:35,780
Brother Lu.

604
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:37,140
You said Rong is on this mountain?

605
00:27:38,620 --> 00:27:41,500
(Bald Wood Peak)
Yes. She's at the mountaintop.

606
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:43,540
This Bald Wood Peak

607
00:27:43,540 --> 00:27:45,020
is several times higher

608
00:27:45,020 --> 00:27:46,440
than the Middle Peak
of Iron Palm Mountain.

609
00:27:47,380 --> 00:27:48,660
How can I climb up

610
00:27:48,940 --> 00:27:50,060
without the help of a rope?

611
00:27:51,420 --> 00:27:52,260
Rong.

612
00:27:54,460 --> 00:27:55,740
Rong.

613
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:56,580
Guo.

614
00:27:57,060 --> 00:27:59,340
I've told you this place.

615
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:00,220
It's up to you

616
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:01,220
how to get up.

617
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:06,860
Rong must be

618
00:28:08,100 --> 00:28:09,620
angry at me because I misunderstood her,

619
00:28:10,700 --> 00:28:12,220
so she left me with a difficult task.

620
00:28:14,020 --> 00:28:15,260
It's killing me

621
00:28:16,020 --> 00:28:17,140
not being able to see her.

622
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:19,300
I'd rather just to climb up.

623
00:28:20,620 --> 00:28:21,980
(Even if I fall and die,)

624
00:28:23,260 --> 00:28:24,860
(it can show my affection to her.)

625
00:28:53,380 --> 00:28:54,660
(Chief Huang just wants him to learn)

626
00:28:54,660 --> 00:28:56,260
(how it feels to be unable to see her.)

627
00:28:56,660 --> 00:28:57,980
(But what if something happens to him?)

628
00:28:58,220 --> 00:28:59,780
(I would become the villain here.)

629
00:29:05,740 --> 00:29:07,740
Guo, please stop.

630
00:29:08,340 --> 00:29:09,980
Watch my method.

631
00:29:11,540 --> 00:29:12,980
Cut off the lamb legs,

632
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:13,940
and while the blood is hot,

633
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:15,500
put it on the mountain peak.

634
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,980
After the blood freezes,

635
00:29:16,980 --> 00:29:18,740
the lamb leg can be frozen on the peak,

636
00:29:19,180 --> 00:29:20,620
and become stronger than steel nails.

637
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:23,220
If you climb it step by step,

638
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:25,380
you can build a ladder.

639
00:29:53,060 --> 00:29:53,900
Rong.

640
00:29:56,260 --> 00:29:57,100
Rong.

641
00:30:02,420 --> 00:30:03,260
Rong.

642
00:30:06,460 --> 00:30:07,300
Rong.

643
00:30:10,180 --> 00:30:11,020
Rong.

644
00:30:11,700 --> 00:30:12,540
It's really you.

645
00:30:20,660 --> 00:30:21,500
What?

646
00:30:22,460 --> 00:30:24,140
During the days you can't see me,

647
00:30:24,420 --> 00:30:26,100
is it not enought for you to call my name

648
00:30:26,100 --> 00:30:27,060
dozens of times a day?

649
00:30:27,060 --> 00:30:27,900
Not enough.

650
00:30:28,260 --> 00:30:29,580
Even if I call your name

651
00:30:29,580 --> 00:30:30,600
a thousand times, it's not enough.

652
00:30:31,300 --> 00:30:32,140
Rong.

653
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:33,300
It's really you.

654
00:30:33,460 --> 00:30:34,300
Great.

655
00:30:37,940 --> 00:30:38,780
By the way,

656
00:30:39,460 --> 00:30:40,500
how did you know?

657
00:30:41,220 --> 00:30:42,300
So you were in my army.

658
00:30:43,620 --> 00:30:45,460
That's because you are too dump.

659
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:47,580
Elder Lu showed it so obviously.

660
00:30:47,820 --> 00:30:49,140
Why did you just realize it?

661
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:51,860
Yes.

662
00:30:53,300 --> 00:30:54,300
I am too dump.

663
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:55,700
Otherwise,

664
00:30:56,140 --> 00:30:57,260
I wouldn't have fallen for Yang Kang

665
00:30:57,260 --> 00:30:58,420
and Ouyang Feng's schemes,

666
00:30:59,260 --> 00:31:00,540
and misunderstood you and Master Huang.

667
00:31:02,540 --> 00:31:03,540
I'm sorry.

668
00:31:07,980 --> 00:31:09,460
I don't know what to do

669
00:31:10,020 --> 00:31:11,220
to make you forgive me

670
00:31:11,900 --> 00:31:13,140
and be willing to see me.

671
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:14,340
Why do I need to see you?

672
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:19,780
If you knew I was safe and alive,

673
00:31:20,340 --> 00:31:21,340
would you agree

674
00:31:21,340 --> 00:31:22,460
to marry Huazheng?

675
00:31:24,620 --> 00:31:26,620
Then I would rather
you don't know my whereabouts.

676
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:30,620
Yes.

677
00:31:31,380 --> 00:31:33,060
No matter what I do now,

678
00:31:33,740 --> 00:31:34,820
I'm sorry for you.

679
00:31:36,460 --> 00:31:37,340
But Rong,

680
00:31:37,900 --> 00:31:38,980
my kindness towards you

681
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:40,500
was all sincere.

682
00:31:40,940 --> 00:31:42,000
Heaven and earth can testify it.

683
00:31:47,300 --> 00:31:49,100
Of course I know your sincerity.

684
00:31:50,140 --> 00:31:51,180
Or why would I look for you?

685
00:32:00,060 --> 00:32:00,900
Rong.

686
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:02,940
How did you escape

687
00:32:02,940 --> 00:32:03,940
from Ouyang Feng?

688
00:32:03,940 --> 00:32:05,380
That's a long story.

689
00:32:05,980 --> 00:32:06,820
On the way,

690
00:32:06,820 --> 00:32:07,940
Ouyang Feng forced me

691
00:32:07,940 --> 00:32:09,460
to explain the Nine Yin Manual to him.

692
00:32:10,540 --> 00:32:12,860
We happened to pass by
Guiyun Manor that day.

693
00:32:13,940 --> 00:32:14,860
I came up with an idea

694
00:32:15,220 --> 00:32:16,420
and forced him to go to Guiyun Manor.

695
00:32:17,140 --> 00:32:18,740
That Old Venomous Creature is arrogant.

696
00:32:19,060 --> 00:32:20,100
He never expected

697
00:32:20,100 --> 00:32:21,860
I used the Eight-Diagram Formation
of Guiyun Manor

698
00:32:22,180 --> 00:32:23,700
to escape from his clutches.

699
00:32:26,980 --> 00:32:28,660
I was planning to return
to Peach Blossom Island.

700
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:30,100
Unexpectedly,

701
00:32:30,100 --> 00:32:31,460
(Dock)
he had already guessed my thoughts

702
00:32:31,650 --> 00:32:33,260
and waited for me at the dock
early in the morning.

703
00:32:34,060 --> 00:32:35,060
I avoided him all the way

704
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:36,220
to the north.

705
00:32:37,220 --> 00:32:38,500
The disciples of the Beggars' Gang said

706
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:39,940
you went to the north.

707
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:41,060
So they were right.

708
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:43,020
It's a pity that when I went there,

709
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:44,380
you had already left.

710
00:32:44,380 --> 00:32:46,060
Ouyang Feng was chasing me closely.

711
00:32:46,620 --> 00:32:48,220
When I heard that
you went to the grassland,

712
00:32:48,460 --> 00:32:49,900
I decided to come and find you.

713
00:32:49,900 --> 00:32:52,180
I even managed to hide
in the Mongol camp.

714
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:53,860
What a pity.

715
00:32:53,860 --> 00:32:55,460
Old Venomous Creature is cunning.

716
00:32:55,460 --> 00:32:56,900
He was also hiding in it.

717
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:59,540
I was afraid of causing you trouble,

718
00:32:59,860 --> 00:33:01,740
so I chose not to see you.

719
00:33:04,580 --> 00:33:05,420
What happened next?

720
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:06,460
Then,

721
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:08,660
I knew you were going to
lead the troops westward.

722
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:10,300
I thought

723
00:33:10,300 --> 00:33:11,860
you were not good at
commanding troops,

724
00:33:11,860 --> 00:33:13,500
and afraid that
you would get yourself killed,

725
00:33:13,860 --> 00:33:15,180
so I found Elder Lu.

726
00:33:15,780 --> 00:33:17,620
He came with a group of disciples
from the Beggars' Gang,

727
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:21,100
partly to deceive Old Venomous Creature,

728
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:22,460
and on the other hand,

729
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:23,660
to give you some advice

730
00:33:23,660 --> 00:33:24,900
and lend you a helping hand.

731
00:33:25,420 --> 00:33:26,780
While Elder Lu

732
00:33:26,780 --> 00:33:27,900
was explaining the mysteries

733
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:29,140
of the Book of Wumu,

734
00:33:29,380 --> 00:33:30,580
I should have guessed it was you.

735
00:33:31,660 --> 00:33:32,820
I'm just too dumb.

736
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:35,180
You are not dumb.

737
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:36,660
Or

738
00:33:36,660 --> 00:33:37,500
how could you

739
00:33:37,820 --> 00:33:39,540
force Elder Lu to tell you

740
00:33:39,540 --> 00:33:40,700
how to get on top of this mountain

741
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:41,540
and see me?

742
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:46,540
Rong.

743
00:33:47,780 --> 00:33:48,620
From now on,

744
00:33:49,500 --> 00:33:50,980
stay by my side.

745
00:33:51,820 --> 00:33:53,220
Don't leave me, okay?

746
00:34:01,460 --> 00:34:02,420
Let me think about it.

747
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:15,980
By the way, Jing.

748
00:34:16,540 --> 00:34:18,060
Do you still remember the essentials

749
00:34:18,060 --> 00:34:19,620
of the chapter of
muscle-bone strengthening

750
00:34:20,180 --> 00:34:21,020
in Nine Yin Manual?

751
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:23,060
I...

752
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:24,500
Why are you so careless?

753
00:34:25,020 --> 00:34:26,900
My dad took a lot of time
to translate it.

754
00:34:26,900 --> 00:34:27,740
The strange words

755
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:29,220
in the last chapter of Nine Yin Manual.

756
00:34:30,620 --> 00:34:32,180
You must learn the Nine Yin Manual.

757
00:34:32,820 --> 00:34:33,740
If you don't understand,

758
00:34:34,620 --> 00:34:36,580
I can slowly translate it for you.

759
00:34:37,460 --> 00:34:38,300
Okay, Rong.

760
00:34:39,060 --> 00:34:39,980
But

761
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:41,540
I am now a military general.

762
00:34:42,020 --> 00:34:43,020
I can't be away for too long.

763
00:34:43,540 --> 00:34:45,300
I need to go back for an hour

764
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:46,500
to deal with military affairs.

765
00:34:46,820 --> 00:34:47,660
Okay.

766
00:34:47,660 --> 00:34:48,980
Then I'll wait for you here.

767
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:50,460
You go back to the military camp.

768
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:52,340
I will write the words on the manual.

769
00:34:53,260 --> 00:34:54,300
When you come back,

770
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:55,180
I will finish it.

771
00:34:55,740 --> 00:34:56,620
No.

772
00:34:56,900 --> 00:34:57,400
Well,

773
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:59,140
going up and down the mountain
is quite troublesome.

774
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:00,900
You'd better come back
to the camp with me.

775
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:02,140
No.

776
00:35:03,820 --> 00:35:05,660
Ouyang Feng is extremely cunning.

777
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:07,660
We can't escape from him
no matter where we go.

778
00:35:09,220 --> 00:35:11,820
But, no matter how cunning he is,

779
00:35:11,820 --> 00:35:13,100
he would never expect

780
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:15,300
we were at the top of this mountain peak.

781
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:17,940
In order to guard against him,

782
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:19,860
we must not take the manual

783
00:35:19,860 --> 00:35:20,940
away from the top of the mountain.

784
00:35:21,260 --> 00:35:22,100
Okay.

785
00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:27,380
It's so cold, Jing.

786
00:35:27,900 --> 00:35:29,180
When you come back,

787
00:35:29,180 --> 00:35:30,580
bring some warm clothes.

788
00:35:31,340 --> 00:35:32,460
Tonight,

789
00:35:32,460 --> 00:35:34,420
we will study the manual here.

790
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:35,780
Okay, Rong.

791
00:35:35,900 --> 00:35:36,900
You wait for me here.

792
00:35:37,980 --> 00:35:39,100
(Young)

793
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:40,540
(but trickery.)

794
00:35:41,100 --> 00:35:43,020
(Then I'll wait for you for an hour.)

795
00:35:56,100 --> 00:35:57,700
So Rong, you were prepared.

796
00:35:59,060 --> 00:36:01,180
I was worried Old Venomous Creature
would follow you here,

797
00:36:01,180 --> 00:36:02,580
so I asked Elder Lu

798
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:03,940
to pour hot oil

799
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:05,420
on these ropes

800
00:36:05,420 --> 00:36:06,460
just in case.

801
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:08,820
Last time, he saw you,

802
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:10,060
so he narrowly escaped.

803
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:12,780
But this time he may not be so lucky.

804
00:36:13,620 --> 00:36:14,940
Let's burn the bridge

805
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:16,820
after we cross it.

806
00:36:16,820 --> 00:36:18,540
Chief Huang, you're wise.

807
00:36:19,060 --> 00:36:21,060
Even with Ouyang Feng's
high martial arts skills,

808
00:36:21,060 --> 00:36:22,180
he won't be able to escape.

809
00:36:22,540 --> 00:36:25,380
He might freeze to death
on the mountaintop.

810
00:36:59,020 --> 00:37:00,140
Young people.

811
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:03,780
You did not honor your words.

812
00:37:06,140 --> 00:37:08,580
Are you bullying
an honest person like me?

813
00:37:09,700 --> 00:37:13,340
You guys wait and see!

814
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:33,700
Yours.

815
00:37:35,060 --> 00:37:36,100
Thank you.

816
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:40,740
Slow down.

817
00:37:45,820 --> 00:37:46,660
Rong.

818
00:37:48,380 --> 00:37:49,220
Jing.

819
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:50,860
You've arrived just in time.

820
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:52,220
I made something delicious for you.

821
00:37:52,660 --> 00:37:53,980
Braised lamb trotters.

822
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:56,540
That bad guy on the mountain will drool.

823
00:37:59,260 --> 00:38:00,140
Smells so good.

824
00:38:03,660 --> 00:38:04,660
What's wrong, Jing?

825
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:07,100
I feel like you're not very happy.

826
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:08,980
The city has been surrounded
by the army for several days,

827
00:38:08,980 --> 00:38:09,980
but we couldn't conquer it.

828
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:12,500
Our troops are facing a shortage of food.

829
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:14,660
The soldiers are suffering
from hunger and cold.

830
00:38:15,340 --> 00:38:16,300
How can I have the mood

831
00:38:16,300 --> 00:38:17,420
to enjoy this delicious food?

832
00:38:19,540 --> 00:38:20,460
It turns out you are

833
00:38:20,460 --> 00:38:21,500
worrying about this.

834
00:38:23,060 --> 00:38:24,700
There is no record in the Book of Wumu

835
00:38:24,700 --> 00:38:25,860
about how to break into the city?

836
00:38:26,140 --> 00:38:27,580
I have been pondering over it for days.

837
00:38:28,620 --> 00:38:29,620
I have read the Book of Wumu

838
00:38:29,620 --> 00:38:30,740
over and over again,

839
00:38:31,540 --> 00:38:33,140
but still can't find a suitable way.

840
00:38:33,420 --> 00:38:34,420
The Book of Wumu

841
00:38:34,420 --> 00:38:35,780
has some clever strategies,

842
00:38:35,780 --> 00:38:37,220
but the cases are all

843
00:38:37,220 --> 00:38:38,340
in the Central Plains.

844
00:38:38,700 --> 00:38:40,660
There's no former example

845
00:38:41,140 --> 00:38:42,460
to conquer a strange city like Samarkand.

846
00:38:42,460 --> 00:38:44,860
It's just a pity that Wanyan Honglie

847
00:38:44,860 --> 00:38:45,940
is still hiding in this city.

848
00:38:47,540 --> 00:38:49,020
But I can only watch him

849
00:38:49,260 --> 00:38:50,100
and do nothing.

850
00:38:50,500 --> 00:38:51,380
Actually

851
00:38:51,580 --> 00:38:53,060
it is not that difficult
to conquer the city.

852
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:55,420
Just get one hundred

853
00:38:55,420 --> 00:38:56,940
skillful martial artists like you

854
00:38:56,940 --> 00:38:58,300
to fly to the top
of the city wall quietly

